{"tid":1069482,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"預測今晚 apple 出iPod touch","createTime":"2019-03-20T04:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T15:09:02.000Z","uid":219232,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"69eb80c5cbbe770116fafa0020fa3d3737f454f4","tid":1069482,"uid":219232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"Apple 近日已經連續兩天分別針對 iPad 以及 iMac 產品線更新，而相關消息指出 Apple 還將繼續於 3 月 20 日稍晚在官網上架新品，而這次的主角可能會是已經四年沒有更新的 iPod Tiuch。<br />\n<br />\n新品三連發？Apple 可能會於 3/20 更新 iPod Touch<br />\n<br />\n今年 1 月左右的時候，就有來自多個供應鍊的消息來源指出 Apple 正在開發新一代 iPod Touch，並且可能會於 2019 年推出。現在則是有更進一步的情報顯示，Apple 將會於 3 月 18 日、19 日、20 日連續三天都在官網上架新產品，而排在 iPad mini、iPad Air 和新款 iMac 之後的最後一款新品，外界預期就會是新款的 iPod Touch。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.tw/tech/talk/1183/5212469/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.tw%2Ftech%2Ftalk%2F1183%2F5212469%2F1%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=c1d5dc07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.tw/tech/talk/1183/5212469/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>BTW, 個人預測今晚8:30 準時出iPod touch ，都會有機會出埋AirPods </strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: red;\">大家是否期待</span></em></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d04691a00f76dfb4e3af3e468f8759de307380","tid":1069482,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"4d0d2816ac16f0c80106f0829188b3aed45e6355","tid":1069482,"uid":13897,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"Airpod2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e984ab8ffde726cb4e2e31a949f8ab86f572382","tid":1069482,"uid":18283,"like":4,"